Sales Ladies
-
Date Posted: 2014/04/29 09:46:43
Ref. JB3045377
Job Description
Looking for Professional Sales Ladies for Tiffany & Co. in Kuwait with the below requirements.
1.	Prepare the boutique for welcoming customers: checking the showcases, displays, monitor cleanliness and tidiness of the boutique at all times, and assure the inventory count.
2.	Reconcile the previous night sales reports
3.	Check the log book /communication book on any pending issue to follow up on
4.	Greeting and welcoming customers, followed by attending the customers and provide excellent customer service and product knowledge
5.	Portraying an immaculate grooming and appearance look
6.	Always being well aware of price and products specifications before communicating it to customers, by first checking the label
7.	Preparing daily sales and cash reports to management
8.	Following the boutique manager instruction /Shift Supervisor, related to cash deposit, money exchange, bank deposit, Contact the Workshop for jewellery repairs, etc.
9.	Maintaining the safe room and boutique displays.
10.	Responding to any management project when assigned (attending events and trainings)
11.	Maintaining, developing and building a strategic relationships with customers
12.	Meeting the monthly sales target as communicated by boutique manager
Skills
- Customer service skills
- Interpersonal communication skills
- People oriented
- Positive attitude
- Be able to network and negotiate
- Team player
Requirements:
•	Carrying at least Secondary School Certificate
•	At least one year of experience in Luxury Retail – Preferable in Jewellery
•	Females only
•	Age from 22 years till 32 years
•	Nationality: Lebanese, Syrian, and Egyptian
•	Transferable residence
