About This Company
As per the far vision and the true intention of the two friends Haj Abdul Rahman Al-Bisher and Haj Zaid Al-Kazemi. The year 1959 has gone carrying to the world the emergence of a new star in the Kuwait market.Al-Bisher & Al-Kazemi Group of companies have successfully positioned itself as a leading group of companies with a number of specialist companies strategically located throughout the country and offering their services to all the retail & wholesale market in the areaFrom a small work shed in the deserts of Kuwait that was to become Shuwaikh industrial area Mr. Abdul Rahman Al Bisher and Mr. Zaid Al Kazemi planned to fulfill their vision of brining Mercedes Benz to Kuwait Then and after a long trip casualed with insistence and conscious from Kuwait , Iraq , Lebanon to Germany and back again through the same to Kuwait With just six cars and five employees Mr. Abdul Rahman Al Bisher and Mr. Zaid Al Kazemi introduced to Kuwait the Automobile that is synonymous with Luxury, Prestige and Value: Mercedes-Benz
